verse = \lyricmode {
  Woe me! Be -- hold my tri -- bu -- la -- tion,
for Mesh -- ech is my hab -- i -- ta -- tion;
near Ke -- dar's tents I'm forced to wan -- der,
where trou -- blous tribes -- men kill and plun -- der.
Too long I have with those re -- si -- ded
who hate all peace and who de -- ride it.
I am for peace; what they ab -- hor is
thus when I speak, they are for war!
}
